My Life is officially made!!! ‘The Breaks’ on The L Word @sho_thelword …little gay me is crying right now!! 😭 This show was/is a massive part of my life when discovering my own sexuality and needing to connect and relate and is so important to our community, I’m sooo happy to have my music on there. Thank you to everyone involved! 💙🥹

#thelword #thebreaks #thelwordgenerationq
I can’t wait for you to hear all this new music! I love sharing demo’s with you allll! 💙 ‘Never Mine To Lose’
When it’s over before it starts! 💔
‘The Breaks’ on @thegooddoctorabc @hulu 💙 Thank you to everyone involved in making this happen!

You guys are amazing! This week & last ‘The Breaks’ was the Top TV Song entering the shazam charts in both the US & Canada! Thank you @theannkline @thegooddoctorabc ❤️ Also ‘Not For Me’ music video hit over 1 Million views on @youtubemusic @youtube !! 🤯
Fingerprints OUT NOW!! Wrote this song with Matt Rist, So happy to see this song out in the world, Hybrid Minds & Grace Grundy killed it! 💙
‘Never Mine To Lose’ out April 14th!! Ahhh I’m so excited for you guys to hear this! ❤️ Pre-Save link in bio!
Never Mine To Lose! ❤️ OUT APRIL 14th PRE-SAVE LINK IN BIO!
Never Mine To Lose - Out April 14th ❤️
3 days till ‘Never Mine To Lose’ is out!! So excited…Pre-Save Link in Bio! ❤️
Use this sound over a memory with someone you miss and never want to lose! ❤️

‘Never Mine To Lose’ is out!! Thank you all for the love so far. This video is from the day we wrote it when I was going through a lot personally. I’m so happy it’s finally out, I hope it helps you guys whoever needs to hear it! ❤️ Massive love to @austinward.wav who spent countless hours listening to me cry and talk about my feelings whilst helping me write this haha you’re the best! ❤️
Thank you for all the love on ‘Never Mine To Lose’ 🤍
Never Mine To Lose - Out Now! 🖤
Joining the ‘This Feeling’ trend over on tiktok with Never Mine To Lose - Keep tagging me in your tiktoks! ❤️😘
Life recently! ❤️ Been so lovely seeing my sister home again after 3.5 years in Australia, meeting my little Nephew for the first time! 🥹 & going to the iconic Abbey Road Studios! 🎶
The most beautiful wedding in Paris! Congratulations @hannahproctor14 & @tommyaldred 🤍

‘I Don’t Know What Love Will Do’ Out September 1st 🖤 I’m so excited for you guys to hear this song, I wrote IDKWLWD with one of my best mates and the most talented artist @jolemusic who I’m so happy to have featured on the track with me & @glvssounds ! Pre-Save link is in my bio 🤍
Went on a cute little dog walk and 2 ladies gave us a bouquet of flowers they made. 🥺🖤
Thank you so much for all the love on ‘IDKWLWD’ this week, massive love to everyone streaming, DSP’s and everyone involved in making this song happen. 🤍
Thank you for all the birthday wishes. ❤️☺️🥹

Amsterdam for the new @jeremyscott x @hyundai.europe reveal. 🖤 

#hyundaiReStyle #Restyle2023

I’m so excited, ever since we wrote this song I’ve imagined it with live strings and live piano so we decided to do a new acoustic version for you all ‘I Don’t Know What Love Will Do’ Acoustic Out November 24th! Pre-Save link in bio! 🖤
‘IDKWLWD’ Acoustic Out 24th November - Pre-Save link in bio 🖤
